Frequently Asked Questions

How old is Markieff Morris?

Markieff Morris is 36 years old.

Where was Markieff Morris born?

Markieff Morris was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania.

When was Markieff Morris born?

Markieff Morris was born on September 2, 1989.

How tall is Markieff Morris?

Markieff Morris is 6-9 (206 cm) tall.

How much does Markieff Morris weigh?

Markieff Morris weighs 245 lbs (111 kg).

Is Markieff Morris in the Hall of Fame?

Markieff Morris is not in the Hall of Fame.

When was Markieff Morris drafted?

Markieff Morris was drafted by Phoenix Suns, 1st round (13th pick, 13th overall), 2011 NBA Draft.

What position does Markieff Morris play?

Power Forward.

What is Markieff Morris' net worth?

Markieff Morris has made at least $55,833,952 playing professional basketball.

How much does Markieff Morris make?

Markieff Morris made $8,600,000 in 2019.

How many rings does Markieff Morris have?

Markieff Morris has won one championship.

What is Markieff Morris' Instagram account?

Markieff Morris is on Instagram at keefmorris5.0.

What schools did Markieff Morris attend?

Markieff Morris attended Prep Charter in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, APEX Academy in Pennsauken, New Jersey and Kansas.

Keef, Smooth, Snoop Dogg are nicknames for Markieff Morris.
